page.title: 01THE PEOPLE OF WYE
page.content: Some of the people do their shopping in Wye and the little shops around. Most of the people who we asked live in Wye and thinks that Wye is nice and peaceful to live in.Some people like the little restaurants and eat very often there.All the shops that we went to,the people who we interviewed were all selfemployed.The porter from Wye College enjoyed his work.Before he worked in Wye College he had worked in the bakery over the road.We interviewed a lady and she said she was a Barmaid.We interviewed a man from the Iron-mongers.
